{"tid":1776362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工展會兩成參展商退展　中華廠商會退回參展費","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T16:00:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"700bece24f4e574011e2946ae6745d55169d0a72","tid":1776362,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"工展會明日開幕，今年有300多間參展商，比去年少百多間。香港中華廠商聯合會行政總裁楊立門說，早前有兩成參展商退展，鑑於社會情況，廠商會向他們退回參展費。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，部分國家對香港發旅遊警示，估計入場外地旅客減少，而以往內地客佔入場人士約兩成，他預料今年很多內地人都不會前來。<br />\n<br />\n有賣海味的參展商說，估計今年生意額只有去年的七成，將多推優惠和新商品，吸引顧客。亦有參展商說，已參展多年，不想今年突然退展，又說不擔心可能出現的遊行示威影響生意。"},{"pid":"394d213b83be669a671ee1256a018d475e7e5954","tid":1776362,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496793-20191209.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496793-20191209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=2d3e45b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496793-20191209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c5fe922b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496793-20191209.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e8b8fa9dfd2fcc3e3c0d1d97ab9cdeda125594f4","tid":1776362,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a38a669153c1038a98e9fe76043737fba290b2","tid":1776362,"uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做得好<br />\n<br />\n幾時腰斬埋成個會期"},{"pid":"aa5b46427fe0509d355a1b5d3e9e834b9601e26e","tid":1776362,"uid":269515,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbRpVVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbRpVVk.png&h=3d9e7c29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05734c95ac8beea7ee9acdc4dd99e3a653ad2bbc","tid":1776362,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"工展會明開鑼 入場需安檢禁帶危險品<br />\n今屆工展會將實施「入場安全檢查」，禁止攜帶具攻擊性或危險物品、具政治色彩的宣傳品及非飲用液體等，以確保參展商、入場人士及員工的安全。<br />\n<br />\n睇新聞話入場都要check手袋同行李<br />\n我心諗去個工展會都咁麻煩 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4d3d959a14d01f88e87362e92b7b5f95d7a4b1","tid":1776362,"uid":27664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估計入場外地旅客減少，而以往內地客佔入場人士約兩成，他預料今年很多內地人都不會前來。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你個閪，要搵大陸人錢就死返上去開舖啦"},{"pid":"5d2d23c8f27f75ae53d26c9afeba1cbd2e735975","tid":1776362,"uid":272119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05734c95ac8beea7ee9acdc4dd99e3a653ad2bbc","tid":1776362,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"工展會明開鑼 入場需安檢禁帶危險品<br />\n今屆工展會將實施「入場安全檢查」，禁止攜帶具攻擊性或危險物品、具政治色彩的宣傳品及非飲用液體等，以確保參展商、入場人士及員工的安全。<br />\n<br />\n睇新聞話入場都要check手袋同行李<br />\n我心諗去個工展會都咁麻煩 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"咁麻煩，不了"},{"pid":"c28e46e259a4bef28305478a060732767d22bdd6","tid":1776362,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de866441555c9cb17542d42accf2350d936ad69f","tid":1776362,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05734c9