834f063b37f9742c41bf3f760e","tid":1776362,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d80b858d195eff3a89359fd3afba13ab49ffc4f","tid":1776362,"uid":261677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fb24d9f34c2dee86e7dbd7a359da6697697d80","tid":1776362,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"火燒又得<br />\n入場踢爛D假景又得<br />\n<br />\n一陣見到肥媽德國寶扯火裝修又得<br />\n<br />\n唔俾拎危險品入?<br />\n一堆人出口入又得"},{"pid":"2745dfef5953de51ad66b334b9f577b059cb7155","tid":1776362,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"中華廠商會好藍"},{"pid":"6bd6cafdad15903e64a480ff384f3ce8607db660","tid":1776362,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n昨日遊行最深刻的一句「初夏&mdash;&mdash;寒冬」<br />\n我們不經不覺由初夏走到冬天<br />\n由撐黃色食店走到黃色經濟圈<br />\n香港人就是有心有力也有財力<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，以往每年聖誕聯歡/Re-U都總係會叫啲最方便快捷嘅KFC、PizzaHut聖誕套餐，今年相信大家都不了不了，所以我地整合左所有會做到會服務嘅黃店，大家識Do啦！<br />\n*（亦建議學生會將圖印出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=ab719896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=508a454e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5</a>"},{"pid":"7497cd31a68dd1e4bd73d05def27beb39cc2eb78","tid":1776362,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"d0bb0279aff25edc788bb0426156716304f107d1","tid":1776362,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5b46427fe0509d355a1b5d3e9e834b9601e26e","tid":1776362,"uid":269515,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbRpVVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbRpVVk.png&h=3d9e7c29&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"1-6？<br />\n好多人番緊工喎"},{"pid":"e03f4e799fa13965a354b798f5848d3b17dac9ab","tid":1776362,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=247abaf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"6a3bc1dcd7af85f8c577cbc68168d58b70ffe0f7","tid":1776362,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0bb0279aff25edc788bb0426156716304f107d1","tid":1776362,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5b46427fe0509d355a1b5d3e9e834b9601e26e","tid":1776362,"uid":269515,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbRpVVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbRpVVk.png&h=3d9e7c29&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"1-6？<br />\n好多人番緊工喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"頓號黎，有咁難睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以1pm和你lunch一轉然後6pm收工後再行一轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}